1. What is the best way to promote your session on the Trailblazer Community, Power of Us Hub, or Partner Community?
Solution : C. Tailor your message to each group you post to, and say why you're excited to be presenting this topic

2. What is the best way to use social channels to interact with your audience?
Solution : D. All of the above

3. What should you do when using streaming video to memorialize your presentation?
Solution : A. Ensure you have enough battery life on your recording device
